dataList.appIntro:
Barcelona Football Theme keyboard theme offers wonderful typing experience and bike drive personalized enjoyment.
How to apply Barcelona Football Theme keyboard theme?
Notice: Barcelona Football Theme theme is a plugin app, please download the Main Keyboard app first for Bike Drive Theme theme to run. Tap the INSTALL button and download it for FREE! If you already have the Main Keyboard installed, please tap on the APPLY button and Barcelona Football Theme theme will be installed on your phone automatically.
Features ??
? Smart Emoji?: 800+ pre-installed emojis! The emojis are supported on all Android devices and other mobile OS. Send and share all kinds of smileys, emoticons, cute and smart emojis easily!
The auto emoticon prediction feature allows you to search for emojis and emoticons in the keyboard area intelligently by typing simple words.
? Theme Center?? Find all sorts of cute and colorful keyboard themes from various categories, including tech, basic, cool, crystal, golden, pink and many more. You can find all the themes you love in the theme center and enjoy the greatest typing experience!
? Compatibility?: Works on all applications, including many popular apps such as Facebook Messenger, Twitter, WhatsApp, WeChat, Google Talk, Line and many more.
? Key-press sound?: Personalize the touch tone of your keyboard with different themes. Realistic keyboard sound effects that are crisp and clear. There are loads more supported themes waiting for you to explore.
? Special Note on Privacy?: You may receive privacy alerts (e.g. Bike Drive Theme keyboard may collect your personal information), these are standard security warnings on all Android OS when enabling third-party apps. Bike Drive Theme keyboard will NOT collect any private or personal information, such as identity info or bank card info etc.
? Supported Languages?: Barcelona Football Theme keyboard theme supports over 80 languages
? Animated themes?: Make your phone unique with all sorts of cool animated effects
? Customizable fonts?: More font styles will be available in Barcelona Football Theme theme very soon
? About Barcelona Football Theme theme:
Want to enter the world of Bike Drive Theme? Hurry up and download Barcelona Football Theme theme IME!
Bike Drive Theme is a 3D button skin pack with cool 3D effects. Bike Drive Theme is also a keyboard theme which has plenty of beautiful Bike Drive Theme wallpapers for your phone's background.
? If you like our app, please do not forget to write comments. Thank you!
This IME theme is my original bike drive keyboard design. I have included 26 specially designed Bike Drive Theme themed icons for the keyboard buttons, such as bike drive styled space bar, bike drive styled Enter button, bike drive styled symbol keys, bike drive styled Delete button and many more. My advanced 3D keyboard design was inspired by Bike Drive Theme designs from other creators. Personally, I love Barcelona Football Theme themed button widgets on the top of the keyboard. If you like bike drive, you will love this colorful theme and it may even surprise you. It also includes other cool themes such as beauty, graffiti, rock singer, love, luxury cars, cartoons, stars, sexy and so on.
Download and apply Barcelona Football Theme theme for free and stylize your Android phone. Thank you for choosing this cool Bike Drive 3D theme. Barcelona Football Theme is designed to let you enjoy a faster and smoother mobile operating experience whether your phone is Samsung, Sony, Huawei, HTC, Xiaomi, Microsoft or any other brands. Handwriting and slide (Swype) input methods will be available soon.
